milestones.description: Mohammad Ishaq and Saleem Raza's 20-run partnership is UAE's highest for the 5th wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 8 between Mazhar Hussain and Saleem Raza
Johanne Samarasekera and Arshad Laeeq's 57-run partnership is UAE's highest for the 7th wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 1 between Johanne Samarasekera and Arshad Laeeq
Johanne Samarasekera and Zarawani's 13-run partnership is UAE's highest for the 8th wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 6 between Arshad Laeeq and Zarawani
Arshad Laeeq has broken the record for playing the most ODIs (2) for UAE, going past Azhar Saeed
